NAME Front Yard
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are standing in front of a house constructed primarily of the same material as the nearby cliffs. Partially obscured by the palms and other local trees, the house appears to belong here, as if it has been here forever. Next to a door constructed of some dark wood is a simple brass plaque.%c
*DESCRIPTION_END

