NUMBER 470
NAME Library
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
Bookcases line the walls of this large room. The exception is the wall to your left, which contains large glass windows looking out onto the garden.  A large desk sits in a corner, covered with books and papers. There is also a couch here. Judging from the number of books lying around, you guess that this room gets a lot of use. The room is designed for comfort; the furniture is old, but comfortable and well taken care of.%c
*DESCRIPTION_END

