NUMBER 471
NAME Garden
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
As you gaze around the garden, a riotous mix of colors assaults your eyes. Taylor and Garin have brought back cuttings and clippings from their journeys, and have raised a garden unrivaled in Fayd. Trees that were thought to grow only in somewhat chillier climes, such as an uquart, grow here thanks to Taylor's skill in magic. Tropical ferns and shrubs grow here as well; you recognize plants that have been transplanted from islands to the south of here. The garden extends a small way towards the sea; there is a path that wanders down to the shore from here.%c
*DESCRIPTION_END

